Query:
SELECT track_name, track_popularity
FROM datawarehouse
ORDER BY CAST(track_popularity AS INT) DESC

SELECT artist_id, AVG(CAST(track_popularity AS INT)) AS avg_track_popularity
FROM datawarehouse
GROUP BY artist_id
ORDER BY avg_track_popularity DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT album_name, release_date
FROM datawarehouse
WHERE release_date > '2020-01-01'

SELECT artist_id, SUM(CAST(followers AS INT)) AS total_followers
FROM datawarehouse
GROUP BY artist_id
ORDER BY total_followers DESC
LIMIT 10

SELECT album_name, COUNT(*) AS track_count
FROM datawarehouse
GROUP BY album_name
